FYI, Duotone Icons Contain 2 Layers!

If you're using unicode values to render icons, like with CSS pseudo-elements, you'll need to use the incode value for each layer. We're showing the rendering of each layer below and the corresponding unicode value separately. It may be a good idea to brush up on duotone icon use and options if you're not too familiar with them yet.
